The Telegraph - Calcutta : Bengal
 Wednesday, March 10, 2004 				 Loot brain held
																								Howrah, March 9: Kurban Ali Mondal, who masterminded dacoities in buses returning from weddings, was arrested in North 24-Parganas last night. He was the principal accused in the bus heists at Jagatballavpur in Howrah last month and Haroa in North 24-Parganas in January.
